I am a data scientist, Tottenham Hotspur fan, Veteran, and proud minivan owner. I created this website to share my work and help future Matt find code snippets and remember how I did things.
I built this site with quarto, and have used it as a chance to revamp an older website built with Hugo & {blogdown}
For information on me, feel free to visit the about_me section to get a brief bio and find links to my LinkedIn, Github page, and current resume.

